<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凌晨，乳梦冰淇淋店的店长迪佩尔小姐来到了店里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她打开了门，然后打开了灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她吓了一大跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的冰淇淋不见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我快要融化了！”玛拉擦着额头说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要说话。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那样只会让你觉得更热。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美罗城小学的空调坏了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾普卡特老师班上的同学们正忍受着炎热。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>本来是安静阅读的时间，但是没有人可以把注意力集中在阅读上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太热了，我都不能思考了。”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是。”杰克说，“我希望我们可以去游泳。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克闭上眼睛，想象着自己跳进一个凉爽的泳池。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望我们可以吃冰淇淋。”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那样我们就可以凉快下来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果火箭女孩儿在这儿就好了。”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她可以帮我们摆脱炎热。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也不是特别热呀。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在开玩笑吧？”特勒尔问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不热吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然热。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我有一个秘诀可以让自己凉快一些。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔一脸好奇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他人也是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是吗？”杰克问，“快告诉我们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克还有玛拉把身子凑了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131942</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看起来很严肃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131943</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以告诉你们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是你们要保证不会告诉任何人。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们保证。”大家屏住呼吸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的。”罗西小声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“其实很简单。当天非常热的时候，我....”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你什么？”玛拉问，“你怎么做？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看了看四周，确保没有人在听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她小声说：“我就尽量不去想它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说完之后，罗西咯咯地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克抱怨道：“我以为你真的要告诉我们什么好办法呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾普卡特老师坐在教室前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抬起头看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道现在很热。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是请保持安静。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还是觉得火箭女孩儿可以帮我们摆脱炎热。”特勒尔小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西听到她的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘是市长。’她心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“艾普卡特老师。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以去一下厕所吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西到了女厕所。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长。”她看着手表的屏幕说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有什么事吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿，我们需要你的帮助！”布洛姆市长说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真实储蓄银行被抢劫了。我已经跟潘校长说过了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在事情解决之前，你可以不用去学校。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我马上过去。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>